<td style="width:20%; text-align:left; font-size:0.9em;">←&#160;<a href="/wiki/%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D_(%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%96%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D)/%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%83_%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%83(%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D)" title="शिशुपालवधम् (मल्लिनाथव्याख्योपेतम्)/नवमः सर्गः(प्रदोषवर्णनम्)">नवमः सर्गः(प्रदोषवर्णनम्)</a>
</td>
<td style="width:60%;"><span style="font-size:110%"><b><a href="/wiki/%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D_(%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%96%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D)" title="शिशुपालवधम् (मल्लिनाथव्याख्योपेतम्)">शिशुपालवधम् (मल्लिनाथव्याख्योपेतम्)</a></b></span><br />दशमः सर्गः(सुरतवर्णनम्)<br /> <a href="/wiki/%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%83:%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%98%E0%A4%83" title="लेखकः:माघः">माघः</a>
</td>
<td style="width:200%; text-align:right;font-size:0.9em;"><a href="/wiki/%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D_(%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%96%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D)/%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%83_%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%83(%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8D)" title="शिशुपालवधम् (मल्लिनाथव्याख्योपेतम्)/एकादशः सर्गः(प्रत्यूषवर्णनम्)">एकादशः सर्गः(प्रत्यूषवर्णनम्)</a>&#160;→
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<table style="width:100%; border-bottom:1px solid #A88; background:#FFFFFF; font-size:0.9em;">

